Definition.WordDefinition: Misread \Mis*read"\, v. t. [imp. & p. p. {Misread}; p. pr. & vb. n. {Misreading}.] To read amiss; to misunderstand in reading. [1913 Webster]
misreading n : misinterpretation caused by inaccurate reading
